trans-unit.source: This method can be overridden in order to change the manner in which the list view is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan åsidosättas för att kunna ändra det sätt som listvyn återges.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Even if the ShouldRenderAsTable method returns `true`, the target device might not support tables, in which case the list view will not be rendered as a table.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Även om metoden ShouldRenderAsTable returnerar `true`målenheten kanske inte stöder tabeller, i vilket fall listvyn inte kan återges som en tabell.

trans-unit.source: The ShouldRenderAsTable method returns a `Boolean` that indicates whether the specified table will fit on the target device screen, whereas the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.Tables%2A> (inherited from <xref:System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities>) of the <xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities> class returns a `Boolean` that indicates whether the device supports tables at all.
trans-unit.target: ShouldRenderAsTable-metoden returnerar en `Boolean` som anger om den angivna tabellen får plats på skärmen mål enhet medan den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.Tables%2A>(ärvt från <xref:System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities>) av den <xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities>klassen returnerar en `Boolean` som anger om enheten har stöd för tabeller alls.</xref:System.Web.Mobile.MobileCapabilities> </xref:System.Web.HttpBrowserCapabilities> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.HttpCapabilitiesBase.Tables%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the list must be rendered as a table; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om listan måste återges som en tabell. Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
